title: Arifureta Shokugyou de Sekai Saikyou: Prologue
content:
Here I go, doing it to myself whirlingly again, but it's no time for complaints now, I have made a grave mistake by watching the main show way back in 2019, I'm already committed, and here goes nothing.

The show does NOT fill me with anything positive, nothing stands out or comes out even when I try to remember what went on in this train wreck, but maybe it's just my brain trying to protect me from trauma at a subconscious level.

This one served as the prologue of the main show, I mean, it's in the name I don't know what to tell ya more, you'dthink they would have already seen this in the show itself but who knows, and quite frankly, who cares? right? I personally was busy blinking at the time because there was nothing better to do.

Nothing to see here, just go on with your day guys.
